{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1698-03_014", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur les Démolitions des Forts du Rhin. Sonnet"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mars 1698 [tome 3], p. 14-16."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Amour du Roy pour ses Peuples, & le desir de leur procurer la Paix l’ayant obligé d’accorder à ses Ennemis la démolition de quelques Forts de l’autre costé du Rhin, & des Ponts de Huningue, de Brisac, & du Fort-Loüis, sur le même Fleuve, M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de Saint Genis, premier Capitaine du Regiment d’Infanterie du Comte de Permangle, qui est en quartier à Hombourg, aprés sa derniére Campagne d’Allemagne, a fait sur ce sujet le Sonnet qui suit."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SUR LES DÉMOLITIONS"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "DES FORTS DU RHIN."}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SONNET."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag":